---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { Brain, AlertCircle, CheckCircle, Info } from 'lucide-react';
---

<BaseLayout>
  {/* Hero Section */}
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-white via-brand-primary-50/30 to-white pt-16 pb-12 md:pt-24 md:pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-6">Relationship Health Assessment</h1>
      <p class="font-serif italic text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-600">
        Evaluate your relationship dynamics and identify areas for growth and improvement
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Main Content */}
  <section class="bg-white py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">

        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="space-y-4 mb-6">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <Info class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-600 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <h2 class="font-bold text-gray-800">About This Assessment</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                  This relationship assessment helps you evaluate the health and quality of your romantic relationship by examining key areas like communication, trust, intimacy, and conflict resolution. Based on relationship research and therapeutic frameworks, it provides insights into your relationship strengths and areas that might benefit from attention.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start">
              <Brain class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-600 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <h2 class="font-bold text-gray-800">What It Measures</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                  The assessment evaluates essential relationship dimensions:
                </p>
                <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1">
                  <li class="flex items-center">
                    <CheckCircle class="h-4 w-4 text-green-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" />
                    <span>Communication patterns and effectiveness</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center">
                    <CheckCircle class="h-4 w-4 text-green-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" />
                    <span>Trust, honesty, and emotional safety</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center">
                    <CheckCircle class="h-4 w-4 text-green-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" />
                    <span>Conflict resolution and problem-solving skills</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center">
                    <CheckCircle class="h-4 w-4 text-green-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" />
                    <span>Emotional and physical intimacy</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center">
                    <CheckCircle class="h-4 w-4 text-green-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" />
                    <span>Mutual support and partnership quality</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center">
                    <CheckCircle class="h-4 w-4 text-green-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" />
                    <span>Shared values and life goals alignment</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start">
              <AlertCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <h2 class="font-bold text-gray-800">Important Note</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                  This assessment provides general insights into relationship health and is not a substitute for professional couples therapy or counseling. Every relationship is unique, and professional guidance can provide personalized support.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Interactive Assessment Coming Soon</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              We're currently updating this assessment tool. In the meantime, you can explore our resources for couples therapy and find qualified relationship counselors who can help strengthen your partnership.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start bg-yellow-50 rounded-lg p-4">
              <AlertCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
              <p class="text-sm text-yellow-700">
                If you're experiencing relationship distress, abuse, or severe communication breakdown, we recommend seeking professional couples therapy or individual counseling to address these concerns.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
              <a href="/tools/matchers/therapy-platform-matcher" class="inline-flex items-center bg-indigo-600 text-white px-6 py-3 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md hover:bg-indigo-700 transition">
                Find a Couples Therapist
              </a>
              <a href="/best/audiences/best-for-couples" class="inline-flex items-center bg-indigo-600 text-white px-6 py-3 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md hover:bg-indigo-700 transition">
                View Best Couples Therapy Options
              </a>
              <a href="/reviews/specialty/couples-therapy" class="inline-flex items-center border-2 border-indigo-600 text-indigo-600 px-6 py-3 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md hover:bg-indigo-50 transition">
                Learn About Couples Therapy
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>